sections.text:
44-5230.Basic health benefit plan, defined.

Basic health benefit plan shall mean a lower cost health benefit plan regulated by the Department of Insurance.

SourceLaws 1994, LB 1222, § 8;Laws 2009, LB154, § 9;Laws 2017, LB644, § 7.
